import * as React from 'react';
import KeyboardSpacer from 'react-native-keyboard-spacer';
import { StyleSheet, Text, View ,TextInput,Button,ImageBackground,ScrollView,SafeAreaView} from 'react-native';
import RowName from '../components/RowName';
import TextInputCalc from '../components/TextInputCalc';
import {Icon } from 'react-native-elements';
import style from '../style';
export default function Claculate() {

    const onClick =(first,second,third)=>{
        return(
<View style={styles.row}>
 <TextInput style={styles.input} placeholder={first} />
<TextInput style={styles.input} keyboardType='numeric' placeholder={second} />
<TextInput style={styles.input} keyboardType='numeric' placeholder={third} />
 </View>
        )
    }
 
    return (
        <ScrollView >
            <View style={styles.container}>
                <View style={styles.Forms}>
                    <RowName Title={'Tools For Production'} first={'Tool Name'} second={'Quantity'} third={'Price'}/>
                    <TextInputCalc first={'tool name'} second={'quantity'} third={'price'} onClick={onClick}/>
            
                </View>

                <View style={styles.Forms}>
                    <RowName Title={'Row Materials'} first={'Material Name'} second={'Quantity'} third={'Price'}/>
                    <TextInputCalc first={'material name'} second={'quantity'} third={'price'} onClick={onClick}/>
                </View>


                <View style={styles.Forms}>
                    <RowName Title={'Employment'} first={'Job Title'} second={'Number'} third={'Salary'}/>
                    <TextInputCalc first={'job title'} second={'number'} third={'salary'} onClick={onClick}/>
                </View>

                <View style={styles.Forms}>
                    
                        <RowName Title={'Other'}/>
                        <View style={styles.row}>
                           <Text>Energy (electrical, fuel)</Text>
                           <TextInput placeholder='Value'/>
                        </View>

                        <View style={styles.row}>
                           <Text>transportation</Text>
                           <TextInput placeholder='Value'/>
                        </View>
                    
                </View>
            </View>
            <KeyboardSpacer/>
    </ScrollView>
          );
      }

      const styles = StyleSheet.create({
        container:{
            paddingTop:40, 
            paddingBottom:40,
            backgroundColor:'white',
            flexDirection:'column',
            alignItems:'center',
            marginBottom:50,
        },

        row:{
            padding:10,
            flex:1,
            flexDirection:'row',
            justifyContent:'space-between',
            borderBottomColor:'#dd4e4e',
            borderBottomWidth:1,
        },

        Forms:{
            borderRadius:15,
            padding:10,
            paddingTop:30,
            paddingBottom:30, 
            backgroundColor:'white',
            height:'auto',
            shadowColor: "#000",
            shadowOffset: {	width: 0,	height: 5,},
            shadowOpacity: 0.28,
            shadowRadius: 5.00,
            elevation: 4,
            marginBottom:20,
            width:'94%',
            backgroundColor:'lightgray'
        },
        row:{
            padding:10,
            flex:1,
            flexDirection:'row',
            justifyContent:'space-between',
            borderBottomColor:'#dd4e4e',
            borderBottomWidth:1,
        },
    
        input:{
            textAlign:'center',
            height:30,
            width:110,
        },
        })
